name: NARNIA: The Lion, The Witch, and The Wardrobe
description: OLDE PINE THEATRE: "Where the movies come alive."Come see Narnia: The Lion, The Witch and The Wardrobe the movie, and experience the live theatrical preshow with in-person appearances by The Lion & The White Witch on stage at the Olde Pine Theatre. There will also be photo opportunity after the movie to take your picture with The Lion & The White Witch.
